OL,5,G1135 Prue Leith's Cotswold Kitchen
OL,6,     FPrue welcomes Ellie Simmonds back
OL,7,     Ffor a second visit to her kitchen
OL,8,     Fafter the two got on so well the
OL,9,     Ffirst time, with the five-time
OL,10,     FParalympic swimming gold medallist
OL,11,     Fbaking a coffee and walnut cake.
OL,12,     FPrue's food hero is a tea producer
OL,13,     Ffrom the Vale of Glamorgan who
OL,14,     Fmakes loose leaf tea and kombucha
OL,15,     Ftea, while he has a versatile
OL,16,     Fbaked feta, roasted tomatoes and
OL,17,     Fgarlic dish on the menu and is
OL,18,     Fpleased when a hack for egg yolks
OL,19,     Fgoes well
