OL,5,G2015 FIFA WC2026: Brazil v Norway
OL,6,     FBrazil v Norway (Kick-off 9.00pm).
OL,7,     FCoverage of the third round-of-16
OL,8,     Fmatch, which takes place at New
OL,9,     FYork/New Jersey Stadium in the
OL,10,     FUSA. Brazil came from behind to
OL,11,     Fbeat Japan 2-1 in injury-time,
OL,12,     Fhaving trailed at the break, with
OL,13,     Fgoals by Casemiro and Gabriel
OL,14,     FMartinelli breaking Japanese
OL,15,     Fhearts. Despite not quite reaching
OL,16,     Ftheir peak yet, Brazil will start
OL,17,     Fas favourites here as they look to
OL,18,     Fmove a step closer towards a first
OL,19,     FWorld Cup triumph since 2002.
OL,20,     FNorway had Erling Braut Haaland to
OL,21,     Fthank for a late winner in their
OL,22,     Flast-32 match against Ivory Coast,
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
